These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, funk, blues, house, indie, hip-hop, gospel
There 7 different types of food: zucchini, radish, nectarine, raspberry, onion, cauliflower, potato
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
House: art-deco, wooden, farmhouse, cottage, gothic-revival, victorian, townhouse
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating raspberry##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the left of the victorian house##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 6. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 8. the cottage house is between the townhouse house and the person eating cauliflower##2
 9. the person eating onion is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
10. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of indie##1
12. the fan of indie is the art-deco house##1
13. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
14. the person eating cauliflower is the farmhouse house##1
15. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating potato##1
16. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
18. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating onion##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Music-Genre      | funk  | hip-hop        | indie | blues      | house     | metal      | gospel     |
| Food   | radish | raspberry         | potato   | zucchini | cauliflower    | onion | nectarine |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| House     | gothic-revival  | victorian         | art-deco     | wooden    | farmhouse | cottage     | townhouse     |

